{"tid":2409884,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"誰知我 上游入貨下游未放定時入貨 [GME]","createTime":"2021-02-16T07:15:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T02:27:20.000Z","uid":107157,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fe70db04af82d87b1a378b247b60f5b4a67c2eaf","tid":2409884,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T07:15:37.000Z","msg":"Wrong hold <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原：隔離<br />\n<br />\n關注他 追看他 在螢幕裡牽掛<br />\n升距被限制嗎 不必怕<br />\nibank 隔絕我跟他 封鎖了嗎 便跌下<br />\n<br />\n十四天 大概足以證實 情商你會自理<br />\n持有 等你short squeeze 一再說起<br />\n<br />\n誰知我 上游入貨下游未放定時入貨<br />\n跌過漲過期待等他深跌再入過<br />\n<br />\n但我偏偏苦等天天溝貨股價繼續挫<br />\n未退出 驚怕什麼<br />\n<br />\n如今我 獨來獨往大時大節未提及過<br />\n試過每晚全面離線未見得更易過<br />\n突然驟降 隔離了我<br />\n阻止我搞清倉<br />\n<br />\n掃貨我極徹底<br />\n管他纏繞到下世<br />\n回復掣 無情被廢<br />\n繼續strong hold 仍不敢放低<br />\n<br />\n＊<br />\n心路歷程 劣改劣唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/r0llingsheep/wrong-hold-gme\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fr0llingsheep%2Fwrong-hold-gme&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2BkuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=5c0006f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/r0llingsheep/wrong-hold-gme</a><br />\n<br />\n有冇同路人完成埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e4ce94c10790bf3db73ee45e2aacafc1cd0185","tid":2409884,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T07:15:59.000Z","msg":"就黎又5點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80a067f783053a2e9a63348ec9759377656a0de6","tid":2409884,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T12:54:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"552f0fd8f1b0a61b5d5d19b1212ba96f2bb3fb18","tid":2409884,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T13:04:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\